# Core Rules

This repository is a static-exported portfolio built with Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript (strict), SCSS Modules, and next-intl.

- Framework: Next.js App Router with static export and base path.
  - See [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) â†’ `output: 'export'` and production `basePath: '/portfolio'`.
- Internationalization: next-intl configured via plugin.
  - See [next-intl.config.ts](mdc:next-intl.config.ts) and [src/utils/request.ts](mdc:src/utils/request.ts).
- SEO defaults live in [src/constants/metadata.ts](mdc:src/constants/metadata.ts).
- Global layout and locale-aware layout live in:
  - [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
  - [src/app/[locale]/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout.tsx)

## TypeScript

- Strict mode is enabled. Avoid `any`; prefer precise types and interfaces.
- Respect path aliases defined in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) (`@/components/*`, `@/utils/*`, etc.).
- Export component props as explicit TypeScript types.

## Styling

- Use SCSS Modules colocated with components (e.g., `Component.module.scss`).
- Keep selectors local; avoid global styles except in [src/styles/app.scss](mdc:src/styles/app.scss).

## Components

- Prefer functional components with explicit `Props` types.
- Images: always use [src/components/common/CustomImage/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/common/CustomImage/index.tsx) to respect production `basePath`.
- Translations: use [src/hooks/useTranslation.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useTranslation.ts) and message files under `public/locales/*`.

## Accessibility & Quality

- ESLint is configured with `plugin:jsx-a11y/strict`, `unicorn`, `sonarjs`, and Prettier.
  - See [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs). Fix all lint errors before committing.

## Commits & Language

- Use Conventional Commits in English (e.g., `feat: ...`, `fix: ...`).
- Any comments inside code must be written in English.
